        <description>&lt;a href="/search/quick?game=Arkanoid"&gt;Arkanoid&lt;/a&gt;-style &lt;a href="/search/quick?game=Breakout"&gt;Breakout&lt;/a&gt; clone, which unlike most other similar games has the bat on the side of the screen (there is a left/right option) instead of at the bottom.  There are 100 screens to be conquered.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;There are a number of types of special bricks, but unlike e.g. Arkanoid, they do not fall towards the bat. Instead, when you hit a special brick, it flips to show a letter. E.g. E (Extend bat), C (Catch ball), M (Missile), B (Bomb, explodes when hit by ball, clearing a number of bricks) and X (Extra life).  Extra lives are also awarded when the player scores 10,000 points.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The enemies/obstacles are more varied than in Arkanoid. Some make the bat freeze, some actually chew and eat your ball and spit out the core back at you!</description>
